<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2551/97 of 15 December 1997 suspending the introduction into the Community of specimens of certain species of wild fauna and flora </inglise>
<eesti> millega peatatakse teatavatest looduslikest looma- ja taimeliikidest isendite &uuml;hendusse sissetoomine 15. detsember 1997 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 9. detsembri 1996. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 338/97 looduslike looma- ja taimeliikide kaitse kohta nendega kauplemise reguleerimise teel (viimati muudetud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2307/97), eriti selle artikli 19 l&otilde;iget 2; </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 338/97 of 9 December 1996 on the protection of species of wild fauna and flora by regulating trade therein (1), as last amended by Commission Regulation (EC) No 2307/97 (2), and in particular point 2 of Article 19 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> p&auml;rast konsulteerimist teadusliku j&auml;relevalver&uuml;hmaga </eesti>
<inglise> After consulting the Scientific Review Group, </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 4 (6) of Regulation (EC) No 338/97 provides for the establishment by the Commission of general restrictions, or restrictions relating to certain countries of origin, on the introduction into the Community of specimens of species listed in Annexes A and B thereto and lays down the criteria for such restrictions; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 338/97 artikli 4 l&otilde;ige 6 n&auml;eb ette, et selle lisades A ja B loetletud liikidest isendite &uuml;hendusse sissetoomisel kehtestab komisjon &uuml;ldised v&otilde;i teatavaid p&auml;ritolumaid puudutavad piirangud ning s&auml;testab selliste piirangute kriteeriumid; n&otilde;ukogu 3. detsembri 1982. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3626/82 (ohustatud looduslike looma- ja taimeliikidega rahvusvahelise kauplemise konventsiooni rakendamise kohta &uuml;henduses) lisas C loetletud liikide suhtes kehtisid &uuml;hendusse sissetoomisel piirangud k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 10 l&otilde;ike 1 s&auml;tete alusel; k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse asendamist m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 338/97 silmas pidades tuleks n&uuml;&uuml;d asjaomaste piirangute aluseks v&otilde;tta viimati nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 6 s&auml;testatud samasugused kriteeriumid; piirangute alla kuuluvate liikide p&auml;ritolumaadega on piirangute vastuv&otilde;tmise asjus konsulteeritud; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas species listed in Annex C to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3626/82 of 3 December 1982 on the implementation in the Community of the Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species of Wild Fauna and Flora (3) were subject to restrictions on the introduction into the Community on the basis of the provisions of Article 10 (1) of that Regulation; whereas, in view of the replacement of that Regulation by Regulation (EC) No 338/97, the restrictions concerned should now be based on the similar criteria laid down in Article 4 (6) of the latter Regulation; whereas the countries of origin of the species subject to those restrictions were consulted with a view to their adoption; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 338/97 artikli 3 l&otilde;ike 2 punktis d on s&auml;testatud, et k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse lisasse B kantakse liigid, mille suhtes on kindlaks tehtud, et elusisendite toomine &uuml;henduse looduskeskkonda kujutaks endast &ouml;koloogilist ohtu &uuml;henduse p&auml;rismaistele looduslikele looma- ja taimeliikidele, mille tulemusena kanti sinna liigid Trachemys scripta elegans ja Rana catesbeiana; k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 6 punktis d on s&auml;testatud, et samasugustel p&otilde;hjustel kehtestab komisjon piirangud selliste liikide &uuml;hendusse sissetoomisel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas point (d) of Article 3 (2) of Regulation (EC) No 338/97 provides for the inclusion in Annex B to that Regulation of species in relation to which it has been established that the introduction of live specimens into the natural habitat of the Community would constitute an ecological threat to wild species of fauna and flora indigenous to the Community, as a result of which the species Trachemys scripta elegans and Rana catesbeiana were so listed; whereas point (d) of Article 4 (6) of that Regulation provides for the establishment by the Commission of restrictions on the introduction into the Community of such species on identical grounds; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 939/97 artikkel 41 sisaldab s&auml;tteid, kuidas komisjoni kehtestatud piiranguid liikmesriikides rakendada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 41 of Commission Regulation (EC) No 939/97 (4) contains provisions for the implementation by the Member States of the restrictions established by the Commission; </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las looduslike looma- ja taimeliikidega kauplemise komitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Committee on Trade in Wild Fauna and Flora, </inglise>
<eesti> on vastu v&otilde;tnud k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Subject to the provisions of Article 41 of Regulation (EC) No 939/97, the introduction into the Community of the specimens of the species of wild fauna and flora mentioned in the Annex to this Regulation is hereby suspended. </inglise>
<eesti> Vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 939/97 artikli 41 s&auml;tetele peatatakse k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas nimetatud looduslikest looma- ja taimeliikidest isendite sissetoomine &uuml;hendusse. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 15 December 1997. For the Commission Ritt BJERREGAARD Member of the Commission </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
